Chet..I guess that is what these pages are all about. Getting other VETS opinions. I appreciate yours. I guess <br>
I wouldn't have made a good wannabe. I always was one to <br>
applaude the guys that could run faster and jump higher <br>
than I could. (Although I do envy the longer lovemaking.)<br>
But I catch your drift, and its a good one. Thank You.<br>
Its been 27 yrs 3 mths back home for me. Feb68-Jan69.<br>
Det. 9, 619th Tac Con Sq. Based out of Saigon. Det.9 was<br>
located in Ban Me Thuot. <br>
My wife and I are going to make our second trip to the<br>
wall the 1st of July. I'll hang in there, because I know<br>
there are brothers like you out there.
